<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.10.2">
<l>viṭantā ṉuṭaiya varavam veruvac ceruvil muṉanāḷmuṉ</l>
<l>taṭantā marainīrp poykai pukku mikka tāṭāḷaṉ</l>
<l>iṭantāṉ vaiyaṅ kēḻa lāki yulakai yīraṭiyāl</l>
<l>naṭantā ṉuṭaiya nāmañ collil namōnā rāyaṇamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you say the name of the one who walked the world with two steps,</l>
<l>The one who dug up the earth as a boar, the one of powerful feet</l>
<l>Who, in combat long ago in front [of all], excelled,</l>
<l>Entering a wide, watery lotus pond to terrify a poisonous snake,</l>
<l rend="indent">[that itself is] the Namō Nārāyaṇam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
